# Negation

.Synopsis
The _not_ operator on Boolean values.

.Syntax
`! _Exp_`

.Types
|====
| ` $Exp$` | `! $Exp$` |
|:---------|:----------|
| `bool`   | `bool`    |
|====

.Function

.Details

.Description
The _not_ operator on Boolean values defined as follows:

|====
| `$Exp$`  | `! $Exp$` |
|:---------|:----------|
| `true`   | `false`   |
| `false`  | `true`    |
|====

.Examples
[source,rascal-shell]
----
!true;
----

